NAME
    Template::Plugin::Hatena - TT plugin for Text::Hatena

SYNOPSIS
      [% USE Hatena -%]
      [% FILTER hatena -%]
      * Hello, World!

      - Good Morning
      -- Greetings

      * Farewell

      - Good Bye
      - Thank you
      [%- END %]

DESCRIPTION
    Template::Plugin::Hatena is a plugin for TT, which format your text with
    Hatena Style.

SEE ALSO
    Template, Text::Hatena

AUTHOR
